
Message reading commands:               Message creation:

AGAIN    - Reread message               FOLLOW   - Reply, with quotes
BACK     - Go back one message          FORWARD  - Forward mail to someone
LIST     - List messages                REPLY    - Send mail to author
NEXT     - Read next message            SEND     - Send new message
VERBOSE  - Redisplay all headers
WRITE    - Save message to a file       Miscellanous commands:

Folder commands:                        CLEAR    - Clear screen
                                        DELETE   - Delete current message
GO       - Go to a different folder     EXPAND   - Expand a mailing list
MOVE     - Move message to a folder     HELP     - Display this menu
                                        QUIT     - Exit mail
